      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I\u2019m looking to find a new home for this awesome ride! It\u2019s been really well-loved and is in great shape for its next adventure. It runs super smoothly, looks sharp, and is totally ready to hit the road today. I've taken great care of it, and I think you're going to absolutely love how it handles! Feel free to reach out if you want to take it for a spin\u2014I'd love to chat and show it to you!",
