      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a prime example of a well-maintained daily driver that balances performance with reliability. The exterior retains a high-gloss finish, though close inspection reveals a few minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear passenger wheel arch\u2014nothing that detracts from its overall sharp appearance. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean and smoke-free. The upholstery is in great shape, with only slight softening of the leather on the driver's seat bolster. All interior features, including the premium audio system, navigation, and heated seats, are fully operational. Mechanically, the car performs beautifully; the engine pulls strongly, and the transmission provides crisp, seamless shifts. It has been serviced strictly according to the manufacturer's schedule, and I have the full maintenance history available for your review. Recent updates include a fresh oil service and a new set of high-performance all-season tires. This car is ready for the road with no immediate maintenance required.",
